OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBright spells and scattered
OL,6,Fshowers, these occasionally heavy
OL,7,Facross the west. Showers will
OL,8,Fgradually die out through the
OL,9,Fafternoon. Fresh westerly winds across
OL,10,Fthe south easing this morning.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRain will spread northeast
OL,13,Ffrom mid-evening. Drier weather
OL,14,Ffollowing on for the early hours.
OL,15,FFresh to strong southwesterly winds
OL,16,Fdeveloping across the far northwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
