OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FWindy with rain at times
OL,6,Facross the west, this turning more
OL,7,Fpersistent later. Dry in the east with
OL,8,Fsome brightness along the Moray coast.
OL,9,FMild.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FCloudy
OL,12,Fand mild with rain on Wednesday, drier
OL,13,Fwith a few showers later. Bright and
OL,14,Fbreezy with showers on Thursday.
OL,15,FChance of rain on Friday, more
OL,16,Fespecially across the south.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
